cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.AI 

The paper deals with image processing and deep learning techniques for the classification of leather defects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of artificial neural networks and convolutional neural networks also suggests that the paper could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), while the pre-processing technique of Canny edge detection could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves classification and efficiency metrics, which could suggest categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
